Package com.ss4group8

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ss4group8.Student
  • public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a student enrolled in a school. A student has studentID, studentName, studentSchool, gender, GPA and year. A student can enroll many courses.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ma Xiao, Fu Mengyan, Kevin Steven Kihata, Ng Chen Ee Kenneth, Ian Tan Yi
